survey_response.review_text: Dr Deepa very polite and caring for her patients, treatment is very satisfying,happy with the way they take care of patients, my mom got implantation and I got alignment treatment, would recommend orthodontist Dr.Karthi , highly appreciated with the hospitality ☺️

I visited the dentist with severe pain in the upper jaw. On taking X ray, it was revealed that one of my teeth was fractured in the root portion. Dr Deepa advised me for removal since the tooth was badly fractured from inside which was not in a  Position to be saved. Consultant was called and the tooth was removed. For a few days, I had problem with having food. But the pain reduced gradually. Am going with the artificial tooth placement next month. Overall, relaxed after visiting here. I recommend this clinic.

got the contact of dr Deepa through practo. i had got a root canal treatment done last year from another dentist but had not placed cap for it. so the tooth got fractured. visited Dr for the cap. Got it done.  Overall good experience with the doctor. Thank you.

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you for the feedback sir. I wish you quit smoking completely .

survey_response.review_text: Am a cigarette smoker since many years. i visited the dentist for dental pain and cleaning. got root canal treatment and cleaning for the teeth. i have reduced cigarette after getting counselled from Dr deepa. i am happy because not only i was treated but was counselled. am preparing my mind for quitting cigarette which am unable to do since many years. i wish i quit completely after some days.

I was facing a bad cheek bite. And pain in the lower teeth.  Dr Deepa suggested for wisdom tooth removal since that was the reason for cheek bite and pain. Got it done from a consultant. I faced swelling for a few days,  now am recovering. Thank you doc *** ********** *****

review_reply.reply_text: Thank you for the feedback sir

survey_response.review_text: from childhood i have dental problems. i have too many cavities. Dr Deepa was suggested by one of my friends. So booked the appointment through practo. she planned my treatment very well. got all the cavity fillings done. i wish i dont get any cavities in future. satisfied with the cost and treatment.

i had spacing in the teeth. i visited the dentist based on practo feedback. this is not the first dentist i have visited so far. when i visited Dr deepas clinic, i was pleased because there was no requirement of braces for me. Instead the gap could be closed with composite filling. i got it done. am happy that i was not pushed to braces treatment like other dentists suggested and am satisfied with my looks now. Thank you doc.

My tooth was broken due to cavity and was painful. Because of the cold weather, pain became very severe and there was a slight swelling also. I got root canal done. Process took more sittings because of the severe infection. Now there is no pain. Should get the cap placed. Thanks to drdeepa for planning the treatment very well.

review_reply.reply_text: Good to hear that sir. Thank you.
